  "text": "Another issue is less control over participants' behavior in this naturalistic design study, and also not controlling for participants breathing patterns during ECG measurement, which could affect HRV results [CITATION_1] . Participants could also fail to mention any conditions or medication in their self-report and, therefore, we need to take these issues into consideration in interpretation of the data.",
